<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Todo App</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Todo App</h1>
    <p>This is a simple Todo app built with React and Material-UI.</p>
    
    <h2>Features</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>View a list of todos</li>
      <li>Add a new todo</li>
      <li>Edit an existing todo</li>
      <li>Remove a todo</li>
      <li>Sort todos by column name</li>
      <li>Filter todos by keyword</li>
      <li>Select a due date for a todo</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>Installation</h2>
    <p>To install and run the app:</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Clone the repository</li>
      <li>Install the dependencies with `npm install`</li>
      <li>Start the app with `npm start`</li>
    </ol>
    
    <h2>Usage</h2>
    <p>To use the app:</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Add a new todo by clicking the 'Add' button and filling out the form</li>
      <li>Edit an existing todo by clicking the 'Edit' button and modifying the form</li>
      <li>Remove a todo by clicking the 'Delete' button</li>
      <li>Sort the todos by column name by clicking on the column header</li>
      <li>Filter the todos by keyword by typing in the search bar</li>
      <li>Select a due date for a todo by clicking on the 'Due Date' field and selecting a date from the calendar</li>
    </ol>
    
    <h2>License</h2>
    <p>This app is licensed under the MIT License.</p>
  </body>
</html>
